title: The Defiance of Duskendale (video)
description:
Barristan's finest hour, or was it? But truly, this story is more about Aerys and Tywin than the great white knight. This episode might cause you to re-think a few things about Robert's Rebellion at the very least. Video available on Spotify. Published October 10, 2020.
